title: Freeman survives tough upbringing to emerge as Falcons star
text:
> Georgia Freeman survives tough upbringing to emerge as Falcons star Atlanta Falcons running back Devonta Freeman (24) runs toward the end zone against the Washington Redskins during the second half of an NFL football game, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Atlanta. Freeman fumbled the ball and = Atlanta Falcons wide receiver Julio Jones recovered for a touchdown. (AP Photo/John Bazemore)
